Following are the details of the Sept.
IGP-M inflation report from the Getulio Vargas Foundation in  Rio
de Janeiro :           NOTE: IGP-M inflation is composed of wholesale Prices (60% weight), 
consumer Prices (30% weight) and construction costs (10% weight).
IGP-M has a final figure and two previews.  The final figure covers
from the 21st of previous month to the 20th of current month.  SOURCE: Getulio Vargas Foundation (FGV)  To contact the reporter on this story:
